      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! \ud83d\ude97 This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells brand new. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. Feel free to come by, take it for a spin, and see just how perfect it is for yourself! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
