    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, this S54-powered icon represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The 3.2L inline-six exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS system overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative measures. Power is routed through a precise six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, providing linear torque delivery and exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring professional subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains its original geometry and damping characteristics. Every component, from the individual throttle bodies to the bushings, remains in concours-level condition, free of any fluid seepage or thermal fatigue.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
