    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes across the bodywork. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creasing or bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting and navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians. It has never seen inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as pristine as the paint. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Includes all original keys, window sticker, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
